<h2>Dark and Stormy</h2>
<img src="dark and stormy.jpg" height=200 width=200 align= "middle">
<h3> Izzi's all time favourite cocktail. Like Ever. </h3>
<h2> Ingredients</h2>
<h3> 50 ml of dark rum </h3>
<h3> 80 ml of ginger beer </h3>
<h3> Dash of lime juice </h3>
<h3> Slice of lime to garnish </h3>

<h2> Instructions </h2>
<h3> Now this one is super tricky. </h3>

<h3> Combine all the ingredients in a tall glass, over ice. </h3>
<h3> Give it a little stir and stick a lime wedge on the side. </h3> 
<h3> Enjoy! Try not to use a straw to save the turtles and other various marine life...</h3>
